# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  "Ask My AI" agent — Google Gemini (free tier, no credit card)
#  1. Get a key: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
#  2. Copy this file to `.env.local` and paste your key below
#  3. Restart the dev server
#  The site works WITHOUT this — the chat widget just shows a setup message.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Optional: override the model without touching code.
# Default is gemini-2.5-flash. Bump to a newer Flash model when available.
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Optional 2nd fallback tier — Groq (free, fast Llama)
#  If Gemini's quota is exhausted, the chat falls back to Groq before
#  using hardcoded answers. Free key: https://console.groq.com → API Keys
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GROQ_API_KEY=
# GROQ_MODEL=llama-3.3-70b-versatile

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Contact form — Web3Forms (free email notifications)
#  Get a free access key at https://web3forms.com (just enter your email).
#  Without it the form gracefully offers a direct-email fallback.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=
